OL,3,CCouncil to spend #440,000 guarding
OL,4,Cempty road
OL,6,FMore than #400,000 is to be spent
OL,7,Fguarding an unfinished road over the
OL,8,Fnext 15 months, to allow repair work
OL,9,Fto be carried out and to protect it
OL,10,Ffrom misuses such as illegal racing.
OL,12,FSwindon Borough Council is paying a
OL,13,Fcontractor #440,000 to guard the
OL,14,FSouthern Connector Road from late
OL,15,FFebruary until mid-2026, allowing work
OL,16,Fto be completed.
OL,18,FThe company building it ` Buckingham
OL,19,FGroup ` went into administration just
OL,20,Fas the road was being completed,
OL,21,Fdelaying its progress.
