OL,3,CCouncil to spend #440,000 guarding
OL,4,Cempty road
OL,6,F"We have a responsibility to get the
OL,7,Froad open, a responsibility to
OL,8,Fcontractors who want to build the
OL,9,Fhouses in the NEV, and a
OL,10,Fresponsibility to residents over in
OL,11,FMerlin Way who are having the
OL,12,Fconstruction lorries use their road
OL,13,Fbecause this road can't be used."
OL,15,FThe council is now waiting for a
OL,16,Fspecialist consultant to explain what
OL,17,Fwork is needed.
OL,19,FIt said the repairs are due to begin
OL,20,Fsoon and are expected to be finished
OL,21,Fby the end of the year.
